name: Nalita
content: Nalita was a human female who lived during the reign of the Galactic Empire. Between 3 ABY and 4 ABY, Nalita and her partner, the bounty hunter Tekrit, traveled to a bar on the Smuggler's Moon of Nar Shaddaa. As Tekrit searched for work to fund the future the pair had planned, a bounty came in for the bounty hunter Boba Fett, who happened to be in the bar at the same time as the pair. Tekrit attempted to claim the bounty, but was killed by Fett.
